{
  "stem": "14190.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I honestly don't think that their children knew that we are Jewish children.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think they were told a-- a story that we are from a different village, that we will be spending summer with them or something like that, some kind of a story.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't believe.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because I'll tell you, if they would have known, that would be-- that would be the end of us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were-- from time to time I-- I heard a Jew here and a Jew there, words that the kids even were saying that they heard what's happening with the Jews.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And would-- they would come and tell the parents.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well, at one point, every Friday there was a marketplace.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was-- usually, that date was a happy time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because, you know, kids were looking forward to go to the market.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they would bring their produce to market.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And also, they would go there to get some things, too.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I overheard the-- the farmer's wife telling him that tomorrow when you go-- and it was early in the morning, usually, when-- when they would go to the marketplace.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Tomorrow, when you go, you take the two-- the two brats to-- to Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I didn't know exactly what's Gestapo, but I knew that it's-- it's affiliated with Nazis.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I-- I knew that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I knew it's not-- that this is not good, that this is something it's-- you give them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And for this, she told him that you're going to get the award.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You're going to get the award, because there was-- apparently, there was a thing that if you-- if you uncover some Jews or bring them to Gestapo, you will get an award.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
